rusty-rain (0.5.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Removed character grouping large-letters (issue #36)

  * Added:
    - Ezemoji dependency for all the characters grouping handling.
    - Cli color option now supports hex color codes.
    - New character grouping opensource
    - New character grouping classic
    - New character grouping pglangs (programming languages)
    - New character grouping numbered-cubes
    - New Config file for character grouping and setting default args

  * Changed:
    - CLI option --characters/-c renamed to --group/-g

  * Fixes:
   - Fixed issue #36 large letter emojis merged into a flags

 -- cowboy8625 <cowboy8625@protonmail.com>  Sat, 16 Aug 2025 20:22:00 +0000

rusty-rain (0.4.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Mostly rewritten code for better readability and performance.
  * Removed itertools dependency; replaced zip! macro with .zip().
  * Fixes:
    - Emojis not working with left and right directions (issue #18).
    - Reduced draw calls (issue #22).
    - Reduced CPU usage (issue #21).

 -- cowboy8625 <cowboy8625@protonmail.com>  Mon, 04 Aug 2025 12:00:00 +0000

rusty-rain (0.3.7-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Replaced ezemoji crate by absorbing its functionality.
  * Added quit with 'q' feature (thanks to hasecilu) (PR #27).
  * Fixed random number generation thread panic (issue #25).

